data.description: This stunning 4-bed, 3-bath home is back on the market! Unveiling craftsmanship at its finest! Sitting on a 1.365 acre corner lot, one of the largest in the neighborhood, it boasts impeccable custom finishes. From the elegant cathedral ceilings with beams to the playroom's charm, every detail is meticulously designed. The chef's kitchen with a pot filler and farmhouse sink is a culinary masterpiece. Create your ideal workspace with this perfect home office! Ample natural light bathes this entire home giving it a warm and inviting feel. This lot has fewer easements than most others in the community making it the perfect place to create your very own backyard oasis! Imagine having an In-law suite, a barn, a pool... whatever you can dream up, it is ready for you! Don't miss your chance to own this showcase of modern farmhouse design, while the builder continues crafting spec homes in the neighborhood.
